summary:
Millina - Brunet Beauty
She is a Nord lvl 1 at the Helgen Keep.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://img836.imageshack.us/img836/4444/millina1s.jpg[/img]

[color=Red][b][u]Millina - Brunet Beauty[/u][/b][/color]
She is a Nord level 1 at the Helgen Keep,
hope you like her, and if you do please leave a comment and endorse 
so other will see her too and so I will see that there is a point to make and share few more..


[color=green][u][b]List of mods that I used: [/b][/u][/color]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666]Official CBBE Face Pack 1-2 and body[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168]ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii[/url]
Think thats all you need to make her look like in the pictures, if you don\'t
get the same look post a pic and I\'ll try to find out :/

[color=yellow][b][u]Also you check my other char Lian: [/u][/b][/color]

[img]http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/1600/lian21s.jpg[/img]

[b][u]You can download her save file here:[/u][/b]
if you want her level 60 all skills unlocked and a lot of money,
get it [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17494]Here[/url]
or if you want her level 1 at the Helgen Keep:
Get it [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17501]Here[/url]



[color=red][i]Anyway, hope you like her![/i][/color]
author: LithiumFlower
